# Polygon 主网 RPC 节点选择规则。
# 维护原则：
# 1) 仅收敛你明确指定的 Polygon 主网 RPC 域名，不扩展为泛区块链代理入口
# 2) 同时保留根域名与通配符子域名，兼顾主机名直连与后续子域名扩展
# 3) 客户端接入时必须放在 proxy/gfw 前，避免被广谱代理规则提前命中

DOMAIN,rpc.sentio.xyz
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.rpc.sentio.xyz
DOMAIN,polygon.llamarpc.com
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.polygon.llamarpc.com
DOMAIN,polygon.drpc.org
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.polygon.drpc.org
DOMAIN,polygon-rpc.com
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.polygon-rpc.com
DOMAIN,polygon-public.nodies.app
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.polygon-public.nodies.app
DOMAIN,polygon-bor-rpc.publicnode.com
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.polygon-bor-rpc.publicnode.com
DOMAIN,poly.api.pocket.network
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.poly.api.pocket.network
DOMAIN,lb.drpc.live
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.lb.drpc.live
DOMAIN,go.getblock.io
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.go.getblock.io
DOMAIN,api.zan.top
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.api.zan.top
DOMAIN,api-polygon-mainnet-full.n.dwellir.com
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.api-polygon-mainnet-full.n.dwellir.com
DOMAIN,1rpc.io
DOMAIN-WILDCARD,*.1rpc.io
